Ehlonna				KEY:Sanctified One ~ Ehlonna					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Class Feature.Sanctified One Class Feature.SpecialQuality																																															DESC:As a sanctified one of Ehlonna, you gain abilities relating to light, life, and nature.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																					SOURCEPAGE:p.100
Light of Life			KEY:Sanctified Ability ~ Light of Life			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Supernatural.Sanctified Ability.Sanctified One Class Feature.SpecialQuality			PREDEITY:1,Ehlonna																																						DESC:Once per day as a standard action, you can call upon Ehlonna's light to create a consecrated area. This effect works like the consecrate spell, except that the effect is mobile and centered upon you. In addition, you are treated as an altar of Ehlonna for the purpose of determining the bonuses granted. This effect lasts for 10 minutes.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																											SOURCEPAGE:p.100
Nature's Bounty			KEY:Sanctified Ability ~ Nature's Bounty			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpellLike.Sanctified Ability.Sanctified One Class Feature.SpecialQuality				PREDEITY:1,Ehlonna																																						DESC:Once per day, you can use heroes' feast (caster level equals 6 + your sanctified one level). Instead of producing tables and chairs, however, this ability produces blankets and pallets more suited to an outdoor setting.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																															SOURCEPAGE:p.100
Nature's Holding			KEY:Sanctified Ability ~ Nature's Holding			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpellLike.Sanctified Ability.Sanctified One Class Feature.SpecialQuality				PREDEITY:1,Ehlonna																																						DESC:Once per day, by touching a plant or a natural earth or stone surface, you create an opening to an extradimensional space similar to that created by a rope trick spell. When you and your allies enter this space and close the "door," no evidence of the opening exists on the outside. The space remains for 12 hours or until the last creature exits, whichever comes first.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																						SOURCEPAGE:p.100
Summon Nature's Mount		KEY:Sanctified Ability ~ Summon Nature's Mount		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpellLike.Sanctified Ability.Sanctified One Class Feature.SpecialQuality				PREDEITY:1,Ehlonna																																						DESC:Once per day as a swift action, you can summon either a unicorn or a griffon (your choice) to serve as your mount. For each sanctified one level you possess, the creature gains 2 Hit Dice and a +2 sacred bonus to its AC. The mount is immune to fear effects, and it remains for 1 hour or until slain. You gain a +5 bonus on Ride checks while riding this creature.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																							SOURCEPAGE:p.100
Fast Healing			KEY:Sanctified Blessing ~ Fast Healing			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Supernatural.Class Feature.Sanctified One Class Feature.SpecialQuality																																													DESC:Once per day as an immediate action, you can gain fast healing 5, which lasts for 10 rounds.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																				SOURCEPAGE:p.100
#
Kord					KEY:Sanctified One ~ Kord					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Sanctified Ability.Sanctified One Class Feature.SpecialQuality																																														DESC:As a sanctified one of Kord, you gain abilities relating to strength and chaos.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																						SOURCEPAGE:p.100
Chaos Warp				KEY:Sanctified Ability ~ Chaos Warp				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Supernatural.Sanctified Ability.Sanctified One Class Feature.SpecialQuality			PREDEITY:1,Kord																																							DESC:Once per day, you can completely ignore all damage from one critical hit scored against you, as well as any effects relating to it.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																														SOURCEPAGE:p.100
Holy Fire				KEY:Sanctified Ability ~ Holy Fire				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Supernatural.Sanctified Ability.Sanctified One Class Feature.SpecialQuality			PREDEITY:1,Kord																																							DESC:Whenever you cast a spell with the fire subtype, you can choose to change all the fire damage it deals into raw divine damage that is treated as good-aligned for the purpose of overcoming damage reduction. This choice must be made at the time of casting.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																									SOURCEPAGE:p.100
Luck of Battle			KEY:Sanctified Ability ~ Luck of Battle			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Extraordinary.Sanctified Ability.Sanctified One Class Feature.SpecialQuality			PREDEITY:1,Kord																																							DESC:Once per day, you can choose to roll twice for any roll normally requiring 1d20 and use the higher of the two results.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																SOURCEPAGE:p.100
Sanctified Strength		KEY:Sanctified Ability ~ Sanctified Strength		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Supernatural.Sanctified Ability.Sanctified One Class Feature.SpecialQuality			PREDEITY:1,Kord																																							DESC:Once per day, you can apply twice your sanctified one level as a sacred bonus to your Strength for 1 round.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																		SOURCEPAGE:p.100
Blessing of Kord			KEY:Sanctified Blessing ~ Blessing of Kord		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Supernatural.Class Feature.Sanctified One Class Feature.SpecialQuality																																													DESC:At dawn every day, you can choose one of the following blessings of Kord, which lasts for 24 hours: +2 bonus to Strength, +2 luck bonus on all saves, or +10-foot bonus to speed. You cannot change this blessing until the next day.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																													SOURCEPAGE:p.100
