Olidammara				KEY:Sanctified One ~ Olidammara				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Sanctified Ability.Sanctified One Class Feature.SpecialQuality																																														DESC:As a sanctified one of Olidammara, you gain abilities relating to luck and stealth.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																						SOURCEPAGE:p.101
Chaos Luck				KEY:Sanctified Ability ~ Chaos Luck				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Supernatural.Sanctified Ability.Sanctified One Class Feature.SpecialQuality			PREDEITY:1,Olidammara																																						DESC:Once per day as an immediate action, you can grant yourself and each of your allies within 30 feet the evasion ability for 1 round. Any recipient of this benefit who already has evasion gains improved evasion instead. Any recipient who already has improved evasion gains no further benefit.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																			SOURCEPAGE:p.101
Good Catch				KEY:Sanctified Ability ~ Good Catch				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Extraordinary.Sanctified Ability.Sanctified One Class Feature.SpecialQuality			PREDEITY:1,Olidammara																																						DESC:Whenever you make a Disable Device check, you can choose to roll a second time before learning the result of your check. If you do so, you must use the result of your second attempt.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																					SOURCEPAGE:p.101
Not in the Face			KEY:Sanctified Ability ~ Not in the Face			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Extraordinary.Sanctified Ability.Sanctified One Class Feature.SpecialQuality			PREDEITY:1,Olidammara																																						DESC:Once per day as an immediate action, you can apply your base Reflex save as a bonus to your Armor Class for 1 minute. Whenever you are denied your Dexterity bonus, you lose this bonus as well.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																				SOURCEPAGE:p.101
Rogues' Blessing			KEY:Sanctified Ability ~ Rogues' Blessing			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Supernatural.Sanctified Ability.Sanctified One Class Feature.SpecialQuality			PREDEITY:1,Olidammara																																						DESC:If you have the sneak attack ability, you gain an extra 1d8 points of sneak attack damage for every two sanctified one levels you possess.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																													SOURCEPAGE:p.101
Fast Talk				KEY:Sanctified Blessing ~ Fast Talk				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpellLike.Class Feature.Sanctified One Class Feature.SpecialQuality																																													DESC:Once per combat encounter, you can make a Diplomacy check as an immediate action to prevent an enemy within 10 feet from attacking you. The foe must be attempting an attack against you at the time you use this ability. If your Diplomacy check result exceeds your opponent's Sense Motive check result by at least 1 for every 3 points of base attack bonus the enemy character possesses, he decides not to attack you (or anyone else) this round. In subsequent rounds, he attacks you only if you attack him first or are the only opponent within sight. If your Diplomacy check fails, the opponent attacks normally, and you cannot use this ability again during this combat encounter.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																			SOURCEPAGE:p.101
#
Wee Jas				KEY:Sanctified One ~ Wee Jas					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Class Feature.Sanctified One Class Feature.SpecialQuality																																															DESC:As a sanctified one of Wee Jas, you gain abilities relating to death, law, and spellcasting.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																				SOURCEPAGE:p.101
Armor of Law			KEY:Sanctified Ability ~ Armor of Law			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Supernatural.Sanctified Ability.Sanctified One Class Feature.SpecialQuality			PREDEITY:1,Wee Jas																																						DESC:If you have an armor bonus (permanent or temporary), it increases by an amount equal to your class level. If you have no armor bonus, you can increase your shield bonus instead. If you have neither, you gain no benefit.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																															SOURCEPAGE:p.101
Death's Cloak			KEY:Sanctified Ability ~ Death's Cloak			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Supernatural.Sanctified Ability.Sanctified One Class Feature.SpecialQuality			PREDEITY:1,Wee Jas																																						DESC:Once per day as a swift action, you can render yourself immune to poison, magic sleep effects, paralysis, stunning, disease, and death effects for 1 minute.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																										SOURCEPAGE:p.101
Sanctified Fall			KEY:Sanctified Ability ~ Sanctified Fall			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Supernatural.Sanctified Ability.Sanctified One Class Feature.SpecialQuality			PREDEITY:1,Wee Jas																																						DESC:If you are reduced to -1 or fewer hit points, or even killed outright by a death effect, you can use an immediate action to either cast a spell or make a single attack. For this action only, you can increase your either your effective caster level or your bonus on attack rolls (your decision) by an amount equal to your sanctified one level.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																											SOURCEPAGE:p.101
Sanctified Spell			KEY:Sanctified Ability ~ Sanctified Spell			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Extraordinary.Sanctified Ability.Sanctified One Class Feature.SpecialQuality			PREDEITY:1,Wee Jas																																						DESC:Once per day, you can increase your effective caster level by an amount equal to your Intelligence bonus (if any) for 1 round.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																															SOURCEPAGE:p.101
Ruby Spell				KEY:Sanctified Blessing ~ Ruby Spell			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpellLike.Class Feature.Sanctified One Class Feature.SpecialQuality																																													DESC:Choose a spell that you can cast from the highest level to which you have access. You can now use this spell as a spell-like ability once per day. Doing so requires no material components, unless those components have a gold piece cost equal to 100 gp or more. You can also still cast this spell normally as part of your normal spell repertoire. Each time you gain a new spellcasting level, you can either retain this spell as a spell-like ability or choose a different one from the highest level you can cast.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																															SOURCEPAGE:p.101

# Shadowspy
Spellcasting			KEY:Shadowspy ~ Spellcasting					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Class Feature.Shadowspy Class Feature.SpecialQuality																																																DESC:At each even-numbered level, you gain new spells per day and an increase in caster level (and spells known, if applicable) as if you had also gained a level in a spellcasting class to which you belonged before adding the prestige class level. You do not, however, gain any other benefit a character of that class would have gained. If you had more than one divine spellcasting class before becoming a shadowspy, you must decide to which class to add each level for the purpose of determining spells per day, caster level, and spells known.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																										SOURCEPAGE:p.106
Aura of Anonymity			KEY:Shadowspy ~ Aura of Anonymity				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Supernatural.Class Feature.Shadowspy Class Feature.SpecialQuality																																														DESC:You leave few impressions upon those you meet, and even fewer upon those unexceptional souls you pass in the street. When you are walking in a crowd of ten or more individuals, you gain a divine bonus equal to your shadowspy level on Disguise and Hide checks.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																													BONUS:SKILL|Disguise,Hide|ShadowspyLVL																					SOURCEPAGE:p.106
Radiance of Pelor			KEY:Shadowspy ~ Radiance of Pelor				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Supernatural.Class Feature.Shadowspy Class Feature.SpecialQuality																																														DESC:Pelor has granted you the power to enhance sources of light so that they shine as brightly as the sun. As a swift action, you can augment any or all light sources within 60 feet (including torches, lamps, lanterns, and campfires, as well as objects that are the target of a light spell and magic weapons that glow). The range of any light source so affected doubles, and the effect lasts a number of hours equal to your shadowspy level, or until the light source is extinguished, whichever occurs first. This ability can be used a number of times per day equal to your Wisdom modifier (minimum once).																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																SOURCEPAGE:p.106
Bonus Feat				KEY:Shadowspy ~ Bonus Feat					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Class Feature.Shadowspy Class Feature.SpecialQuality																															DEFINE:ShadowspyFeatPool|0													DESC:At 2nd level and every 3rd level thereafter, you can select a bonus feat for which you meet the prerequisites from the following list: Acrobatic, Alertness, Athletic, Combat Casting, Deceitful, Extra Turning, Improved Turning, Investigator, Good Devotion (see page 58), Persuasive, Stealthy.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																															BONUS:VAR|ShadowspyFeatPool|(ShadowspyLVL+1)/3													SOURCEPAGE:p.106
Immunity to Blindness		KEY:Shadowspy ~ Immunity to Blindness			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Supernatural.Class Feature.Shadowspy Class Feature.SpecialQuality																																														DESC:Beginning at 2nd level, you cannot be blinded by magical effects, spells, or bright light. Physical barriers to sight, such as blindfolds and solid objects, still prevent you from seeing. Additionally, any wounds that cause the destruction of your eyes still blind you.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																							SOURCEPAGE:p.106
Veil of Pelor			KEY:Shadowspy ~ Veil of Pelor					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpellLike.Class Feature.Shadowspy Class Feature.SpecialQuality																																														DESC:When you attain 3rd level, your motives and morality become almost impossible to determine. As an immediate action, you can use undetectable alignment, as the spell (caster level equals your character level). This ability is usable at will.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																												SOURCEPAGE:p.106
Personal Eclipse			KEY:Shadowspy ~ Personal Eclipse				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Supernatural.Class Feature.Shadowspy Class Feature.SpecialQuality																																														DESC:Beginning at 4th level, you can manipulate the direction and intensity of light. By redirecting and dimming ambient illumination, you can cast shadows around your body to better conceal your presence. Doing so grants you a circumstance bonus equal to one-half your shadowspy level on Hide checks. This ability can be used at will but is effective only in areas where light is present.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																				SOURCEPAGE:p.106
Truth of the Light		KEY:Shadowspy ~ Truth of the Light				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpellLike.Class Feature.Shadowspy Class Feature.SpecialQuality																																			SPELLS:TIMES=ShadowspyLVL|TIMES=1|CASTERLEVEL=ShadowspyLVL|Zone of Truth	DESC:When you attain 6th level, creatures in your company find it difficult to tell deliberate untruths. At will, you can use zone of truth, as the spell (caster level equals your character level). You can use this ability a number of times per day equal to your shadowspy level.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																						SOURCEPAGE:p.106
Blinding Light			KEY:Shadowspy ~ Blinding Light				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Supernatural.Class Feature.Shadowspy Class Feature.SpecialQuality																													DEFINE:BlindingLightDC|0													DESC:At 7th level, you learn to blind nearby foes with a brief but intense flash of light. Twice per day, you can project a beam of light from your palm in a cone-shaped burst with a range of 15 feet. Any creature in the area that fails a Reflex save DC %1 (DC 10 + shadowspy level + Wis modifier) is blinded for 1d6 rounds. Sightless creatures are not affected by this ability.|BlindingLightDC																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																												ABILITY:Ability Focus|AUTOMATIC|Blinding Light																																																																																																																																												BONUS:VAR|BlindingLightDC|2|PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=FEAT,Ability Focus (Blinding Light)	BONUS:VAR|BlindingLightDC|10+ShadowspyLVL+WIS	SOURCEPAGE:p.106
Sun's Revelation			KEY:Shadowspy ~ Sun's Revelation				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Supernatural.Class Feature.Shadowspy Class Feature.SpecialQuality																																														DESC:At 8th level, you become adept at detecting untruths spoken in your presence. At will, you can use discern lies, as the spell (caster level equals your character level).																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																							SOURCEPAGE:p.106
Hide in Plain Sight		KEY:Shadowspy ~ Hide in Plain Sight				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Supernatural.Class Feature.Shadowspy Class Feature.SpecialQuality																																														DESC:Beginning at 9th level, you can use the Hide skill even while being observed, as long as you are in a sunlit location. See the ranger class feature (PH 48).																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																										SOURCEPAGE:p.106
Vision of Pelor			KEY:Shadowspy ~ Vision of Pelor				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Supernatural.Class Feature.Shadowspy Class Feature.SpecialQuality																																			SPELLS:Innate|TIMES=3|CASTERLEVEL=ShadowspyLVL|True Seeing		DESC:At 10th level, you can see through even the most potent illusions. Three times per day, you can use true seeing at will, as the spell (caster level equals your character level).																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																						SOURCEPAGE:p.106

# Shadowstriker
Badge of Office			KEY:Shadowstriker ~ Badge of Office				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Extraordinary.Class Feature.Shadowstriker Class Feature.SpecialQuality																																													DESC:Upon your induction into the shadowstrikers, you were given a special holy symbol combining the symbols of Heironeous and Pelor. This item is crafted from gold, inlaid with platinum lightning motifs, and encrusted with sunstones. In areas where the Church of Heironeous or the Church of Pelor holds political power, this badge allows you access to prohibited areas and gives you the right to detain and question suspects in the pursuit of your deity's will.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																							SOURCEPAGE:p.108
Luminous Weapon			KEY:Shadowstriker ~ Luminous Weapon				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Supernatural.Class Feature.Shadowstriker Class Feature.SpecialQuality																																													DESC:You can imbue your melee weapon with the power of the Shining One. When you do so, your weapon glows as if affected by a light spell and gains a bonus equal to twice your shadowstriker level on damage rolls against evil and/or undead creatures. You can use this ability a number of times per day equal to your Wisdom modifier (minimum once), and the effect lasts for 10 rounds.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																					SOURCEPAGE:p.108
Smite Evil				KEY:Shadowstriker ~ Smite Evil				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Supernatural.Class Feature.Shadowstriker Class Feature.SpecialQuality																																													DESC:Beginning at 2nd level, you can smite evil once per day (see the paladin class feature, PH 44). Smite evil attempts/day attained from multiple sources stack.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																		ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Smite Evil																																																																																																																																												BONUS:VAR|SmiteEvilTimes|1																SOURCEPAGE:p.108
Sun's Blessing			KEY:Shadowstriker ~ Sun's Blessing				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Supernatural.Class Feature.Shadowstriker Class Feature.SpecialQuality																																													DESC:When you reach 2nd level, you can cause your weapon to flare with the fires of the sun. As long as the sun's blessing remains upon your luminous weapon, it deals an extra 1d6 points of fire damage. Additionally, the blinding light spilling from the weapon counts as a daylight spell for the duration of the effect. The sun's blessing can be used once per day, and the effect lasts for a number of rounds equal to your shadowstriker level. You can gain an additional use per day of this ability for each daily turn attempt, smite evil attempt, or spell slot (if you are a spontaneous caster) that you sacrifice.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																														SOURCEPAGE:p.108
Surge of Piety			KEY:Shadowstriker ~ Surge of Piety				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Supernatural.Class Feature.Shadowstriker Class Feature.SpecialQuality																																													DESC:When you attain 3rd level as a shadowstriker, your touch becomes infused with positive energy. Any undead creature that touches you (by hitting you in melee or for any other reason) is shaken for 1 round or until it is no longer in physical contact with you-even if it normally can't be affected by this condition. Once per day as a fullround action, you can channel this energy into a single burst of positive energy, which manifests as a flash of bright, warm sunlight. In addition to functioning as a consecrate spell, this wave of energy deals 1d8 points of positive energy damage to every undead creature within 30 feet (no save). You can increase the damage this effect deals by 1d8 points (maximum +5d8) for each daily turn attempt, smite evil attempt, or spell slot (if you are a spontaneous caster) that you sacrifice.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																										SOURCEPAGE:p.108

# Squire Of Legend
Spellcasting			KEY:Squire of Legend ~ Spellcasting				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Class Feature.Squire Of Legend Class Feature.SpecialQuality																																															DESC:At 2nd and 3rd level, you gain new spells per day and an increase in caster level (and spells known, if applicable) as if you had also gained a level in a spellcasting class to which you belonged before adding the prestige class level. You do not, however, gain any other benefit a character of that class would have gained. If you had more than one spellcasting class before becoming a squire of legend, you must decide to which class to add each level for the purpose of determining spells per day, caster level, and spells known.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																											SOURCEPAGE:p.110
Paragon's Path			KEY:Squire of Legend ~ Paragon's Path			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Class Feature.Squire Of Legend Class Feature.SpecialQuality																																															DESC:Upon becoming a squire of legend, you must choose one of the legendary Six from Shadow after whom to model your skills and abilities. Once made, your choice cannot be changed.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																						SOURCEPAGE:p.110
Save Bonus				KEY:Squire of Legend ~ Save Bonus				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Extraordinary.Class Feature.Squire Of Legend Class Feature.SpecialQuality																											DEFINE:SquireOfLegendSaveBonus|0												DESC:At 1st level, you gain a +1 bonus on a saving throw determined by your paragon, as given on the following table. This bonus increases to +2 when you attain 3rd level.	DESC:&nl;Patron Saving Throw	DESC:&nl;Dardallion Reflex|PREDEITY:1,Dardallion	DESC:&nl;Imdastri Will|PREDEITY:1,Imdastri	DESC:&nl;Ktolemagne Will|PREDEITY:1,Ktolemagne	DESC:&nl;Orsos Fortitude|PREDEITY:1,Orsos	DESC:&nl;Reikhardt Will|PREDEITY:1,Reikhardt	DESC:&nl;Sunyartra Fortitude|PREDEITY:1,Sunyartra																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																		BONUS:SAVE|Reflex|SquireOfLegendSaveBonus|PREDEITY:1,Dardallion	BONUS:SAVE|Fortitude|SquireOfLegendSaveBonus|PREDEITY:1,Orsos,Sunyartra	BONUS:SAVE|Will|SquireOfLegendSaveBonus|PREDEITY:1,Imdastri,Ktolemagne,Reikhardt								BONUS:VAR|SquireOfLegendSaveBonus|1+(SquireOfLegend>2)											SOURCEPAGE:p.110
Squire's Burden, Least		KEY:Squire of Legend ~ Squire's Burden (Least)		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Supernatural.Class Feature.Squire Of Legend Class Feature.SpecialQuality																																													DESC:You gain the first of several supernatural abilities that let you use the skills of your chosen paragon to aid others. Unless otherwise noted, each paragon's gift (least, lesser, and greater) requires a swift action to invoke, lasts for a number of rounds equal to twice your squire of legend level, is usable once per day, and has a caster level equal to three times your squire of legend level. When the description of a squire's burden ability specifies an ally, it means only an ally; you cannot use the effect on yourself unless so stated.	DESC:&nl;Dardallion: You can grant yourself and one ally flanking bonuses against a foe that both of you threaten, even if you are not properly positioned to flank. The bonus persists as long as you both threaten that enemy.	DESC:&nl;Imdastri: You can use sanctuary, as the spell.	DESC:&nl;Ktolemagne: You can use comprehend languages, as the spell.	DESC:&nl;Orsos: You can use speak with animals, as the spell.	DESC:&nl;Reikhardt: You can grant one ally within 30 feet the ability to take an immediate action of a specified type out of turn. If you invoke this ability as a swift action, the ally can take a 5-foot step. If you invoke it as a move action, she can take a move action. If you invoke it as a standard action, she can take a standard action.	DESC:&nl;Sunyartra: As an immediate action, you can negate a single critical hit against one ally within 30 feet. The ally still takes normal damage from the hit.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																												SOURCEPAGE:p.110
Squire's Burden, Lesser		KEY:Squire of Legend ~ Squire's Burden (Lesser)		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Supernatural.Class Feature.Squire Of Legend Class Feature.SpecialQuality																																													DESC:At 2nd level, you gain a new supernatural ability that you can use once per day. This ability follows all the guidelines for least squire's burden (above), unless otherwise noted. If you choose, you can forgo your daily use of this ability for an extra use of your least squire's burden.	DESC:&nl;Dardallion: As an immediate action, you can grant one ally within 30 feet the opportunity to reroll a saving throw, skill check, or ability check.	DESC:&nl;Imdastri: You can use shield other, as the spell. The effect lasts for a number of rounds equal to three times your squire of legend level.|PREDEITY:1,Imdastri	DESC:&nl;Ktolemagne: You can use see invisibility, as the spell. The effect lasts for a number of rounds equal to three times your squire of legend level.|PREDEITY:1,Ktolemagne	DESC:&nl;Orsos: You can use lesser restoration, as the spell.|PREDEITY:1,Orsos	DESC:&nl;Reikhardt: You can grant an ally within 30 feet a second use of an extraordinary or supernatural ability normally usable only once per day. If you gain a second daily use of this ability, you cannot use it twice in one day on the same ally.|PREDEITY:1,Reikhardt	DESC:&nl;Sunyartra: You can use true strike, as the spell, but only on a single ally within 30 feet.|PREDEITY:1,Sunyartra																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																														SOURCEPAGE:p.110
Faithful Companion		KEY:Squire of Legend ~ Faithful Companion			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Extraordinary.Class Feature.Squire Of Legend Class Feature.SpecialQuality																																												DESC:At 3rd level, you learn to place yourself between an ally and harm. If you and an ally within 5 feet are both subject to an area spell or effect that allows a Reflex save for partial damage, you can grant your ally a bonus on her saving throw by taking a penalty of equivalent magnitude on your own. The value of the bonus and penalty can be any amount up to the value of your base Reflex saving throw. You must decide to invoke this ability before either you or your ally has attempted the saving throw.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																SOURCEPAGE:p.110
Squire's Burden, Greater	KEY:Squire of Legend ~ Squire's Burden (Greater)	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Supernatural.Class Feature.Squire Of Legend Class Feature.SpecialQuality																																													DESC:At 3rd level, you gain a new supernatural ability you can use once per day. It follows all the guidelines for least squire's burden, above. If you choose, you can forgo your daily use of this ability for an extra use of the least or lesser squire's burden.	DESC:&nl;Dardallion: You can grant one ally within 30 feet the ability to move through threatened areas without provoking attacks of opportunity for 2 rounds. Other actions, such as casting in a threatened area, still provoke attacks of opportunity as normal.|PREDEITY:1,Dardallion	DESC:&nl;Imdastri: You can grant one ally within 30 feet immunity to one of the following effects for a number of rounds equal to three times your squire of legend level: disease, exhaustion/ fatigue, mind-affecting spells and abilities, negative levels, or poison. You choose the effect when you activate this ability.|PREDEITY:1,Imdastri	DESC:&nl;Ktolemagne: As a swift action, you can take over concentrating to maintain an ally's spell or spell-like ability, allowing her to take other actions. Once you have assumed control of an effect, you cannot give it back.|PREDEITY:1,Ktolemagne	DESC:&nl;Orsos: You can grant one ally within 30 feet energy resistance 10 to an energy type of your choice for a number of rounds equal to three times your squire of legend level.|PREDEITY:1,Orsos	DESC:&nl;Reikhardt: When an ally within 30 feet of you uses an extraordinary, spell-like, or supernatural ability that affects all allies within a given number of feet, you can use an immediate action to extend its range and duration by 50%%.|PREDEITY:1,Reikhardt	DESC:&nl;Sunyartra: As an immediate action, you can grant one ally within 30 feet the opportunity to reroll an attack roll or critical hit confirmation roll.|PREDEITY:1,Sunyartra																																																																																																																																																																																												SOURCEPAGE:p.111


