ST|CLASS=Ranger;LEVEL=2|-100	BONUS:SPELLCAST|CLASS=Ranger;LEVEL=3|-100	BONUS:SPELLCAST|CLASS=Ranger;LEVEL=4|-100					BONUS:VAR|ChampionOfTheWildFeatCount|(RangerLVL>3)+(RangerLVL>7)+(RangerLVL>10)+(RangerLVL>13)	COST:0			SOURCEPAGE:p.50
