Wolf Totem				KEY:Spiritual Totem ~ Wolf			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Barbarian Class Feature.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																						DESC:The wolf is a loyal ally who uses pack tactics to subdue her foes. If you choose her as your spiritual totem, you gain an additional +2 bonus on attack rolls when flanking an opponent.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																						SOURCEPAGE:p.46	ASPECT:CombatBonus|gain an additional +2 bonus on attack rolls when flanking an opponent.
