Spiritual Connection		KEY:Ranger ACF ~ Spiritual Connection	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Ranger Class Feature.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																									SPELLS:Class|TIMES=3|CASTERLEVEL=RangerLVL|Speak with Animals|Speak with Plants	DESC:You learn to speak with spirits of the wild places. Although this ability does not automatically make such spirits well disposed toward you, it does provide several benefits. You can use speak with animals and speak with plants as the spells (caster level equals your ranger level). You can use any combination of these effects up to three times per day. This replaces Wild Empathy.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																					SOURCEPAGE:p.50
Spiritual Guide			KEY:Ranger ACF ~ Spiritual Guide		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Ranger Class Feature.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																									SPELLS:Class|TIMES=1|CASTERLEVEL=RangerLVL|Commune with Nature				DESC:You are befriended by a spiritual guide that speaks to you and aids you as long as you remain in the wilderness.  As long as you are in the wilderness you gain a bonus of %1 on Handle Animal, Knowledge (Nature), Listen, Search, Spot, and Survival checks. In addition you can use commune with nature, as the spell, once per day (caster level equals your ranger level). This replaces your animal companion.|SGSkillBonus																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																															SOURCEPAGE:p.50
Antiquarian				KEY:Rogue ACF ~ Antiquarian			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Rogue Class Feature.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary																																							DESC:You are incredibly knowledgeable about artifacts, relics, and antiques-especially those that are religious in nature. When examining magic items created with divine spells, you add your Wisdom modifier to your Appraise checks. Additionally, 1/day you can make a Knowledge (Religion) check (DC 10 + item's caster level) to identify a magic item per the identify spell with your caster level equal to your rogue level.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																															SOURCEPAGE:p.51
Death's Ruin			KEY:Rogue ACF ~ Death's Ruin			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Rogue Class Feature.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																							DESC:You can channel the power of your faith when making sneak attacks against undead and deal 1/2 your normal sneak attack damage.  This supernatural ability replaces the trap sense class feature at all levels.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																		SOURCEPAGE:p.51

# How are these added?
Friend's Evasion			KEY:Rogue ACF ~ Friend's Evasion		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Rogue Class Feature.RogueAbilities.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary	!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Improved Evasion																										DESC:Every ally adjacent to you benefits from your evasion ability.  If you take this ability, you no longer can take Improved Evasion.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																															SOURCEPAGE:p.51
